<form id="commission" action="/commission" method="post">
    <h2>Commission the Artist Herself!</h2>

    <p>Fill out the form below to get started on your commission. Paiten will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
    <p>Note: All commissions are subject to Paiten's availability and discretion. Please be patient as she reviews your request.</p>
    <label for="name">Your Full Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required><br><br>

    <label for="email">Your Email:</label>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required><br><br>

    <label for="phone">Your Cellphone Number:</label>
    <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required><br><br>

    <label for="message">What do you want (Please be specific):</label>
    <textarea id="message" name="message"></textarea><br><br>

    <input type="submit" value="Submit for Consideration">
</form>